prompt: Summarize the following story in first person: The memorable day i found so unforgettable is my cousins birthday, each moment i look into the eyes of my beloved girl friend i seem to replay all the event of that day all over again. At evening as people get around to start the jamz, i suddenly sited a lady, so elegant and sparkling at the corner of the room. i was dazed at such beauty. I ask my cousin Sarah who she was, i was informed of how great Linda is.  I was so desperate to be around her and setup a conversation.  Sarah made a quick introduction which set me on a good to start gist. she was so lovely to be with. And till now she is my lovely baby girl.
